N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 330.7 - Committee chair and secretary

State Regulations

The chair shall designate a member of the Psychology

Practice Committee to serve as chair of the committee, and shall also appoint a
secretary of such committee. Notes
